nodes.text: The Clone Wars: Stories of Light and Dark (audiobook)

The Clone Wars: Stories of Light and Dark is an unabridged audiobook of the canon anthology book The Clone Wars: Stories of Light and Dark, which contained stories written by Jason Fry, Lou Anders, Preeti Chhibber, Anne Ursu, Yoon Ha Lee, Tom Angleberger, Zoraida Córdova, Rebecca Roanhorse, Sarah Beth Durst, Greg van Eekhout, and E. Anne Convery. The audio book features narration from Catherine Taber, James Arnold Taylor, Corey Burton, Matt Lanter, Nika Futterman, Sam Witwer, and Olivia Hack. It was published on August 25, 2020.
